('isomorphic-labs', 'Isomorphic Labs', 'DeepMind spinout applying AI to drug discovery with AlphaFold-powered biology',
 E'Isomorphic Labs is a DeepMind spinout company that applies AI to drug discovery, built on the foundation of AlphaFold - the protein structure prediction system that the scientific community has described as the most significant advance in structural biology in fifty years. Where AlphaFold solved the protein folding problem, Isomorphic Labs applies the underlying AI capabilities to the broader drug discovery pipeline: understanding how small molecules interact with proteins, predicting the structural consequences of mutations, and designing new drug candidates with optimal target engagement properties.\n\nThe company operates as a fully integrated AI drug discovery organization rather than a platform provider. Isomorphic Labs runs internal drug discovery programs and enters large-scale collaboration agreements with pharmaceutical companies - Eli Lilly and Novartis each signed agreements worth up to $3 billion in 2024, the largest AI drug discovery partnerships ever announced. These collaborations involve Isomorphic applying its AI capabilities to multiple drug targets across oncology, cardiovascular, and other disease areas with milestone and royalty payments tied to clinical development progress.\n\nFor the pharmaceutical industry, Isomorphic Labs represents the clearest signal of where AI drug discovery is heading: not incremental improvement of existing workflows but complete reimagination of molecular biology from first principles using the models that have already demonstrated superhuman performance on protein structure prediction. The platform is not commercially licensed as a standalone product - access is through co-development partnerships structured at the enterprise level. Academic and independent biotech teams interested in AlphaFold-derived capabilities can access the public AlphaFold protein database but not the proprietary Isomorphic drug discovery platform.',
 'https://isomorphiclabs.com', 'https://isomorphiclabs.com',
 'paid', false, NULL, 4.7, 410, false, false, false,
 ARRAY['biotech', 'drug-discovery', 'ai-research'],
 ARRAY['Built on AlphaFold breakthrough - the most significant structural biology advance in fifty years', 'Eli Lilly and Novartis partnerships worth up to $3B validate the platform at the highest commercial level', 'DeepMind parentage provides access to frontier AI research capabilities not available to competitors', 'Integrated drug discovery organization - not just a software tool - aligns incentives with clinical outcomes'],
