 ARRAY['Platform is a partnership and collaboration model - not a self-serve computational biology tool', 'Generative protein design is emerging - clinical proof-of-concept for internally designed proteins is still pending', 'Biologic manufacturing and clinical development costs are identical to traditional protein therapeutics', 'Highly specialized for protein therapeutic discovery - not applicable to small-molecule or RNA programs'],
